N2  - The article presents news and notes from the Academy of Management as of June 1965. A meeting of the Eastern Management Association at the Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania is scheduled for May 7 and 8. Recipients of the Richard D. Irwin Foundation Doctoral Fellowships for 1965-66 include Frederick M. Adler, Donald Erienkotter, and Herbert E. Kierulff. Other news is presented.
